  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Implementation of strengthening and training mechanisms for the economic reintegration of former combatants</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In supporting the Agency for Reincorporation and Normalization (ARN) to develop a method for responding quickly and effectively to requests madeby employers involved in on-going programming, a Tailored Training Strategy is being designed and implemented. It prioritizes areas in part according to the presence of illicit crops, as a method of promoting alternative, licit sources of income. A second stage of the Strategy will facilitate the development of training projects to strengthen capacities of and promote linkages between service providers,the private sector and host communities.</narrative>
  </description>
